    {
      "segments": [
        {
          "scid": "sn35.167:1.1",
          "pli": "Atha kho aññataro bhikkhu … pe … ",
          "en": "Then a mendicant went up to the Buddha … "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn35.167:1.2",
          "pli": "etadavoca: ",
          "en": "and said to him: "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn35.167:1.3",
          "pli": "“kathaṃ nu kho, bhante, jānato kathaṃ passato attānudiṭṭhi pahīyatī”ti? ",
          "en": "“Sir, how does one know and see so that view of self is given up?” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn35.167:1.4",
          "pli": "“Cakkhuṃ kho, bhikkhu, anattato jānato passato attānudiṭṭhi pahīyati. ",
          "en": "“Mendicant, knowing and seeing the eye, sights, eye consciousness, and eye contact as not-self, view of self is given up. … "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn35.167:1.5",
          "pli": "Rūpe anattato jānato passato attānudiṭṭhi pahīyati. ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn35.167:1.6",
          "pli": "Cakkhuviññāṇaṃ anattato jānato passato attānudiṭṭhi pahīyati. ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn35.167:1.7",
          "pli": "Cakkhusamphassaṃ anattato jānato passato attānudiṭṭhi pahīyati. ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn35.167:1.8",
          "pli": "Yampidaṃ cakkhusamphassapaccayā uppajjati vedayitaṃ sukhaṃ vā dukkhaṃ vā adukkhamasukhaṃ vā tampi anattato jānato passato attānudiṭṭhi pahīyati … pe … ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn35.167:1.9",
          "pli": "jivhaṃ anattato jānato passato attānudiṭṭhi pahīyati … pe … ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn35.167:1.10",
          "pli": "manaṃ anattato jānato passato attānudiṭṭhi pahīyati. ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn35.167:1.11",
          "pli": "Dhamme … ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn35.167:1.12",
          "pli": "manoviññāṇaṃ … ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn35.167:1.13",
          "pli": "manosamphassaṃ … ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn35.167:1.14",
          "pli": "yampidaṃ manosamphassapaccayā uppajjati vedayitaṃ sukhaṃ vā dukkhaṃ vā adukkhamasukhaṃ vā tampi anattato jānato passato attānudiṭṭhi pahīyatī”ti. ",
          "en": "And also knowing and seeing the pleasant, painful, or neutral feeling that arises conditioned by mind contact as not-self, view of self is given up.” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn35.167:1.15",
          "pli": "Dvādasamaṃ. ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn35.167:1.16",
          "pli": "Nandikkhayavaggo paṭhamo. ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn35.167:2.1",
          "pli": "Nandikkhayena cattāro, ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn35.167:2.2",
          "pli": "jīvakambavane duve; ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn35.167:2.3",
          "pli": "Koṭṭhikena tayo vuttā, ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn35.167:2.4",
          "pli": "micchā sakkāya attanoti. ",
          "en": ""
        }
      ],
